Package: ec-connect
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: docker-ce | docker.io, zenity
Recommends: xclip | xsel
Maintainer: 厚皮龙 <huang.wenlong@synthoid.ai>
Homepage: https://github.com/WenlongHuangResearch/easyconnect_linux
Description: EasyConnect VPN GUI Launcher
  A user-friendly graphical launcher for Sangfor EasyConnect VPN,
  running in Docker with socks5 and HTTP proxy support.
  .
  基于 Docker 的深信服 EasyConnect VPN 图形化启动器。
  支持 Zenity 弹窗交互登录，自动提供 socks5 和 HTTP 代理。
